text: Gârbova may refer to the following places in Romania: * Gârbova, a commune in southern Alba County * Gârbova de Jos, a village in the municipality Aiud, northern Alba County * Gârbova de Sus, a village in the municipality Aiud, northern Alba County * Gârbova (Mureș), a river in northern Alba County * Gârbova (Secaș), a river in Sibiu and Alba Counties
title: Gârbova (disambiguation)
